			(property "Description" "HDMI Type-A receptacle, 19 signal pins + SH (shell). Electrical pinout per the public HDMI spec (manufacturer-independent). Footprint: real, verified part -- Amphenol ICC (FCI) 10029449-001RLF family (confirmed on DigiKey, in stock), footprint copied from KiCad's own Connector_Video.pretty library (HDMI_A_Amphenol_10029449-x01xLF_Horizontal), pad names cross-checked (1-19 + SH) against the symbol's pin numbers. Supersedes an earlier unverified 'Amphenol GSD1S211-K1E1-4030' claim -- that part number never corroborated in search and should be treated as wrong."
				(at 0 0 0)
				(show_name no)
